News.headline: Elite Team College Academy Update
News.short_description: Elite Team have now won three out of three games in the season leaving them top of the National League U19 Alliance.
News.description:
The College Academy have beaten Boreham Wood FC 2-0, Romford FC 5-1 and Grays Athletic 4-1. 

The Academy top goalscorers for the College Academy so far are Christian Baxanean and Jonathon Olaoye who both have three goals to their name. 

The next fixture for the College Academy is the National League Cup game vs Chesham United (Home).
